OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,FA judge-led public inquiry into the
OL,7,FNottingham attacks victims will take
OL,8,Fplace in 'a matter of weeks', the
OL,9,FPrime Minister has confirmed.
OL,11,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia, was
OL,13,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,14,Forder after killing 19-year-old
OL,15,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,16,FO'Malley-Kumar and 65-year-old
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023.
OL,19,FThree other people were seriously
OL,20,Finjured when Calocane, took Mr Coates
OL,21,Fvan and drove at them in Nottingham.
