OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,FThe families of the Nottingham attacks
OL,7,Fvictims had met with the Prime
OL,8,FMinister, the Home Secretary, the
OL,9,FHealth Secretary and the Attorney
OL,10,FGeneral today (February 12th).
OL,12,FEmma Webber, the mother of Barnaby
OL,13,FWebber, said she expected an inquiry
OL,14,Fto be confirmed during the meeting at
OL,15,FNumber 10, describing it as a
OL,16,F"watershed moment for this case".
