OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,FSpeaking outside Number 10, Mrs Webber
OL,7,Fsaid: "So, it is the first bit of
OL,8,Fpositive news we've been able to have
OL,9,Ffor a very, very long time. Still
OL,10,Fprocessing it."
OL,12,FDr Kumar also spoke and confirmed the
OL,13,Fpublic inquiry will take place in the
OL,14,F'next few weeks'. He said: "As we have
OL,15,Falways said as families, everywhere
OL,16,Fthat Valdo Calocane intersected with
OL,17,Fthe authorities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
