OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F374A1739450805
OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,F"We were let down by those authorities
OL,7,Fand today the Prime Minister confirmed
OL,8,Fwe are going to have a public inquiry
OL,9,Fthat will be statutory and have powers
OL,10,Fto call people and the judge will be
OL,11,Fable to call witnesses up and we will
OL,12,Fbe able to get answers to all of the
OL,13,Fmany questions that we've got there
OL,14,Fhas been fantastic news for all of us.
OL,16,F"We welcome it and we have been
OL,17,Fworking so hard towards it and I just
OL,18,Fthink we couldn't be more delighted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
