OL,6,FThe son of Ian Coates, James Coates
OL,7,Fsaid: "Last week there weren't many
OL,8,Fpositive emotions you could bring out
OL,9,Fof that meeting and I widely express
OL,10,Fthat myself.
OL,12,F"But, today is finally a good reason
OL,13,Fto come to London and to get some good
OL,14,Fwords, to get the promises we were
OL,15,Fgiven and now we can see changes.
OL,17,F"It is not just about us and our
OL,18,Ffamilies and victims, it is about the
OL,19,Ffuture and public and protecting the
OL,20,Fpublic, so they don't have to walk in
OL,21,Four shoes and can feel safe."
