OL,6,FDowning Street previously said Sir
OL,7,FKeir is committed to a judge-led
OL,8,Finquiry and has not ruled out a public
OL,9,Finquiry with full statutory powers.
OL,11,FTheir meeting with the PM followed the
OL,12,Fpublication of NHS England's report
OL,13,Finto the mental health care received
OL,14,Fby Calocane in the lead up to the
OL,15,Fattacks on February 5th.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
