OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,F"Nationally, we have asked every
OL,7,Fmental health trust to review these
OL,8,Ffindings and set out action plans for
OL,9,Fhow they treat and engage with people
OL,10,Fwho have a serious mental illness,
OL,11,Fincluding how they work with other
OL,12,Fagencies such as the police.
OL,14,F"And we've instructed trusts not to
OL,15,Fdischarge people if they do not attend
OL,16,Fappointments.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
