OL,6,FMarjorie Wallace, chief executive of
OL,7,Fmental health charity SANE, as
OL,8,Ffamilies of victims of the 2023
OL,9,FNottingham attacks press Prime
OL,10,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer for a
OL,11,Fstatutory public inquiry.
OL,13,F"We support the families of Barnaby
OL,14,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and Ian
OL,15,FCoates, in their campaigning for the
OL,16,Ftruth and their passion that the loss
OL,17,Fand grief that they have suffered
OL,18,Fshould not happen to others.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
