OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F374A1739450805
OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Cto take place in 'matter of weeks'
OL,6,F"Having been involved in inquiries for
OL,7,Fover three decades, it is unacceptable
OL,8,Fthat families should have to go to
OL,9,Fthese lengths to find out the
OL,10,Fcircumstances of their relatives'
OL,11,Fdeaths and the ways in which they
OL,12,Fcould have been prevented.
OL,14,F"We can only hope that this watershed
OL,15,Ffight for justice will actively compel
OL,16,Fmental health trusts to respect and
OL,17,Finvolve families before and when a
OL,18,Ftragedy occurs and include their
OL,19,Fconcerns in patients' care plans and
OL,20,Frisk assessments."
